dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents areas of aggregated socioeconomic and demographic information at the NUTS 1 level for Europe. NUTS 1 units have an average population between three million and seven million people. NUTS (Nomenclature des Unit√©s Territoriales Statistiques) refers to the Nomenclature of Territorial Units for Statistics. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2.Europe NUTS 1 Demographics provides NUTS 1 level demographic information for Europe.
